uration-300 group-hover/link:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground hover:opacity-60 transition-all relative group/link pointer-events-auto\" href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-0.5 bg-foreground transition-all duration-300 group-hover/link:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground hover:opacity-60 transition-all relative group/link pointer-events-auto\" href=\"#services\">Services<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-0.5 bg-foreground transition-all duration-300 group-hover/link:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground hover:opacity-60 transition-all relative group/link pointer-events-auto\" href=\"#video-showcase\">VFX Showreel<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-0.5 bg-foreground transition-all duration-300 group-hover/link:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground hover:opacity-60 transition-all relative group/link pointer-events-auto\" href=\"#contact\">Get in touch<span class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-0.5 bg-foreground transition-all duration-300 group-hover/link:w-full\"></span></a></nav><div class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center transition-opacity duration-300 pt-24 md:pt-40 lg:pt-48\" style=\"opacity:1\"><h1 class=\"hero-name-custom text-2xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3 md:mb-6 cursor-pointer glitch-container group/name\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-montserrat)\"><span class=\"glitch-text\" data-text=\"Aashish Thakur\">Aashish Thakur</span></h1><div class=\"space-y-1 md:space-y-2 mb-6 md:mb-12\"><p class=\"hero-title-custom text-base md:text-xl text-muted-foreground\">Director &amp; VFX </p><p class=\"hero-subtitle-custom text-sm md:text-lg text-muted-foreground font-semibold\">Innovator &amp; Design Thinker</p><p class=\"hero-description-custom text-sm md:text-lg text-muted-foreground\">Building AI-powered healthcare solutions</p></div><button class=\"space-y-3 md:space-y-4 group cursor-pointer text-left focus:outline-none\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-4\"><h2 class=\"hero-cta-custom text-xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 origin-left\">Let&#x27;s create</h2><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"hero-cta-custom text-foreground md:w-6 md:h-6 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:-translate-y-2\"><line x1=\"7\" y1=\"17\" x2=\"17\" y2=\"7\"></line><polyline points=\"7 7 17 7 17 17\"></polyline></svg></div><div class=\"h-1 w-20 md:w-32 transition-all duration-500 ease-out group-hover:w-32 md:group-hover:w-48\" style=\"background-color:currentColor\"></div></button></div><div id=\"me\"></div><div class=\"relative mt-8 lg:absolute lg:bottom-0 lg:left-0 lg:right-0 p-4 md:p-8 lg:p-16 lg:mt-0 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px);pointer-events:none\"><div class=\"space-y-2 md:space-y-6\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground leading-tight\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-montserrat)\">AASHISH THAKUR</h2><p class=\"text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground tracking-wide\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-montserrat)\">DIRECTOR &amp; VFX ARTIST</p><p class=\"text-xs md:text-base lg:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-wrap\">Aashish Thakur is an aspiring innovator, developer, and design thinker passionate about building technology that solves real-world problems. Currently working on MediTrack+ and GlucoTrack+, focusing on AI-powered healthcare solutions, while also exploring web development, cloud technologies, and product design.</p><p class=\"text-xs md:text-base lg:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed font-semibold\">7 years</p><div class=\"pt-2 md:pt-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-foreground/10 text-foreground border border-foreground/20 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">After Effects</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-foreground/10 text-foreground border border-foreground/20 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">Cinema 4D</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-foreground/10 text-foreground border border-foreground/20 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">React</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-foreground/10 text-foreground border border-foreground/20 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">Next.js</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section id=\"portfolio\" class=\"lg:min-h-screen bg-background text-foreground py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-16 transition-colors duration-300\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"transition-all duration-700\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(100px)\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-foreground mb-12 md:mb-16 lg:mb-20\">Portfolio</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6\"><div class=\"group overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(180px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg\"><img alt=\"GAYAK Movie Poster - Cinematic VFX Design\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:grayscale\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/poster-1.jpg\"/></div></div><div class=\"group overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(190px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg\"><img alt=\"GAYAK Movie Poster - Visual Effects Showcase\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:grayscale\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/poster-2.jpg\"/></div></div><div class=\"group overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(200px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg\"><img alt=\"GAYAK Movie Poster - Ensemble Cast\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:grayscale\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/poster-4.jpg\"/></div></div><div class=\"group overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(210px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg\"><img alt=\"GAYAK Movie Poster - Sunset Composition\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:grayscale\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/poster-3.jpg\"/></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"video-showcase\" class=\"lg:min-h-screen bg-black py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-16\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"transition-all duration-700\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(240px)\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-4 md:mb-6\">VFX Showreel</h2><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-2xl\">A glimpse into my visual effects and title design work for film productions.</p></div><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-video w-full overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-2xl shadow-black/50 group bg-black\"><video src=\"https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/VFX%20-%20Title-B0g7yQ6SdCb5QxXL7uDiv15fRt6ivl.mp4\" autoPlay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsInline=\"\" preload=\"auto\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:scale-105 opacity-100 z-10\"></video><video src=\"https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/new-SBns0FE4ozZLwbRCVRt68AHyxp2ESR.mp4\" poster=\"/images/gayak-thumbnail.webp\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsInline=\"\" preload=\"metadata\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:scale-105 opacity-0 z-0 pointer-events-none\"></video><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none z-20\"></div><button class=\"absolute z-30 left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100\" aria-label=\"Previous video\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"absolute z-30 right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100\" aria-label=\"Next video\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"mt-6 md:mt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Studio Signature Sequence</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Visual Effects &amp; Motion Design</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 text-white text-sm rounded-full\">After Effects</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 text-white text-sm rounded-full\">VFX</span></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 hidden lg:flex gap-4 justify-center\"><button class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 ring-2 ring-white scale-105\"><div class=\"w-32 md:w-40 aspect-video bg-gray-800 relative\"><img alt=\"Studio Signature Sequence\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/vfx-thumbnail.png\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/30\"></div></div><p class=\"text-xs text-white mt-2 text-center truncate px-1\">Studio Signature Sequence</p></button><button class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 opacity-50 hover:opacity-80\"><div class=\"w-32 md:w-40 aspect-video bg-gray-800 relative\"><img alt=\"GAYAK - Title Sequence\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/gayak-thumbnail.webp\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/30\"></div></div><p class=\"text-xs text-white mt-2 text-center truncate px-1\">GAYAK - Title Sequence</p></button></div><div class=\"mt-6 flex lg:hidden flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-full border transition-all duration-300 active:scale-95 bg-white text-black border-white\">Studio Signature</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-full border transition-all duration-300 active:scale-95 bg-black text-white border-white/20 hover:border-white/50 hover:bg-white/10\">GAYAK</button></div></div></div></section><section id=\"services\" class=\"lg:min-h-screen bg-background text-foreground px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-20 transition-colors duration-300\"><div class=\"max-w-[1600px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 md:mb-24\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(223.33333333333334px)\">Services</h2></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"space-y-4 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(350px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-300 dark:text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-black dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300\">01</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground\">VFX &amp; Video Editing</h3><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Professional visual effects, compositing, color grading, and cinematic video editing for films, commercials, and digital content.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(362.5px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-300 dark:text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-black dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300\">02</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground\">UI/UX Design</h3><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Creating intuitive and visually stunning user interfaces with a focus on user experience and modern design principles.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(375px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-300 dark:text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-black dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300\">03</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground\">Web Development</h3><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Full-stack web development using modern technologies, building scalable and performant web applications.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(387.5px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-300 dark:text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-black dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300\">04</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground\">Brand Identity</h3><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Developing distinctive visual identities through logo design, color systems, and cohesive brand assets.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(400px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-300 dark:text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-black dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300\">05</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground\">Consulting</h3><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Technology and creative consulting to help guide your digital transformation and creative projects.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(412.5px)\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-300 dark:text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-black dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300\">06</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground\">Motion Graphics</h3><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Dynamic motion graphics and animations for engaging visual storytelling and brand communication.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"lg:min-h-screen bg-black text-white px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-20\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-8 md:mb-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(306.6666666666667px)\">Start Your Project</h2><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-2xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(360px)\">Let&#x27;s collaborate and bring your ideas to life. Select your project details below.</p><form class=\"space-y-10 md:space-y-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(380px)\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"space-y-3 group\"><label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 group-focus-within:text-white transition-colors\">Name</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full bg-transparent border-b-2 border-gray-700 focus:border-white py-3 text-lg md:text-xl outline-none transition-all duration-300 disabled:opacity-50\" placeholder=\"Your name\" name=\"name\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-3 group\"><label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 group-focus-within:text-white transition-colors\">Email</label><input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full bg-transparent border-b-2 border-gray-700 focus:border-white py-3 text-lg md:text-xl outline-none transition-all duration-300 disabled:opacity-50\" placeholder=\"your@email.com\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><label class=\"block text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400\">Project Type</label><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 md:gap-4\"><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"py-3 md:py-4 px-4 border text-center font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer select-none rounded-md border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/50 text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-500 hover:text-white\">VFX &amp; Animation</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"py-3 md:py-4 px-4 border text-center font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer select-none rounded-md border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/50 text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-500 hover:text-white\">UI/UX Design</button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"py-3 md:py-4 px-4 border text-center font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 cur